embeds.title: Massey Game Jam IV - Results
embeds.description:
The Massey Game Jam IV Winners are:
:first_place: Paranormal Entities by AI Hack (4)
:second_place: A Walk In The Dark by Such_Nick (1)
:third_place: What is that? by MiniGloathj (3)

Congratulations to the top 3 games! We've also posted the information for this game jam in the <#743132168972402759> channel.
